" />"},{"pid":"01a6d29781136f40be0acb3496102076d4eba7b1","tid":1796653,"uid":73293,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T18:03:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nmZMWXp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnmZMWXp.jpg&h=aea5dd1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當黑警短短在數個月，<br />\n周圍舉槍指著市民已成常態，<br />\n有些香港人亦已習慣，<br />\n但其實我們不應該習慣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T7c3eJ5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT7c3eJ5.jpg&h=4e089378&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43525aa6e4b2f83ed278dccbcbfd710146e6a2c3","tid":1796653,"uid":73293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T18:04:26.000Z","msg":"平安夜一向多年來，<br />\n在旺角、尖沙咀、銅鑼灣也會有很多不同的香港人報佳音。<br />\n但今年2019年，卻換來黑警舉旗舉槍，<br />\n甚至以催淚煙阻止市民參與報佳音。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KMDNGrH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKMDNGrH.jpg&h=4e8e19a5&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F432vj3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF432vj3.jpg&h=01ec3374&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sfAwoE4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsfAwoE4.jpg&h=a417df18&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bxaz5Tp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBxaz5Tp.jpg&h=b7d0caeb&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yhtuaj5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhtuaj5.jpg&h=1a6ff461&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b2b9bed70067dff52d6a4ff0d25c2892a0620998","tid":1796653,"uid":73293,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T18:05:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8ZXR78c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8ZXR78c.jpg&h=a5e3abc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JpcOqUT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJpcOqUT.jpg&h=969aa144&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"69aa38ddb47a6a60591ed2ee07682bde7a217f19","tid":1796653,"uid":73293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T18:05:53.000Z","msg":"12月24日 朗豪坊商場內<br />\n黑警以警棍不斷嘔打市民<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CC8U5U6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCC8U5U6.jpg&h=8650bdb4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cpMrW2h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcpMrW2h.jpg&h=4f75f1e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n亦以胡椒噴霧不斷噴向記者<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f9Pw78U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff9Pw78U.jpg&h=482f8cd5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e28173b59a6a40af30b21f7926ab281bb04b056c","tid":1796653,"uid":73293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T18:06:41.000Z","msg":"今年的平安夜<br />\n是多麼的不平安<br />\n是否黑警想以催淚彈呼喚耶穌下來？<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XRLgzPV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXRLgzPV.jpg&h=64cc34e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n水炮車2號在尖沙咀 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tfouaof.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTfouaof.jpg&h=bbc77012&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a95aaff58562063010d48b3eafcafc9bf6d9f8b","tid":1796653,"uid":73293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T18:07:12.000Z","msg":"迷霧漫漫的The One<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QYiaEg1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQYiaEg1.jpg&h=4cf2cfa1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n餐廳內的職員與食客也受影響<br />\n真正想攪炒的其實是黑警和林鄭<br />\n沒有他們的加持<br />\n如何能令商店馬上關門？<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r3CVQoG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr3CVQoG.jpg&h=c5ae5841&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8a5f57706a442c7071e888868bc61409b851e98","tid":1796653,"uid":73293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T18:07:39.000Z","msg":"踏入聖誕節<br />\n以往也是倒數聲和歡呼聲<br />\n今年卻是無數開槍聲<br />\n以及市民恐慌和痛苦的叫聲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3HXOqYj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3HXOqYj.jpg&h=9c11f352&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n黑警再一次射記者眼"},{"pid":"58ae5acd836ba520ed924db77d766c6142203d8c","tid":1796653,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T18:08:22.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n------<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港獨立 唯一出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0ddf30e17a2207f287c30226422ed5dab52df9c","tid":1796653,"uid":73293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8a5f57706a442c7071e888868bc61409b851e98","tid":1796653,"uid":73293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T18:07:39.000Z","msg":"踏入聖誕節<br />\n以往也是倒數聲和歡呼聲<br />\n今年卻是無數開槍聲<br />\n以及市民恐慌和痛苦的叫聲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3HXOqYj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3HXOqYj.jpg&h=9c11f352&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n黑警再一次射記者眼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T18:08:42.000Z","msg":"星島日報記者頭部中胡椒彈<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HZUtrmc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHZUtrmc.jpg&h=ff5c942b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b84e9f09166ffb66c9ed5c21da6f067e2408c6f0","tid":1796653,"uid":73293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T18:09:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dQ3U6sS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdQ3U6sS.jpg&h=09e736c6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e7d7c49e25be232d1d93777cd5e3352fd5096c66","tid":1796653,"uid":73293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T18:11:13.000Z","msg":"2019平安夜之沙田區<br />\n這些人不是示威者，而是便衣黑警<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iWSF1yo.jpg\" 